Merkel Calls for ‘Political Courage’ on Europe, DPA Reports

-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 
2011-11-30T19:06:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-30/merkel-calls-for-political-courage-on-europe-dpa-reports.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel 
called for “political courage” for closer cooperation among
countries that share the euro, Deutsche Presse Agentur reported.  Merkel repeated that “limited” treaty changes should be
ratified by euro-area member states to that end, DPA said. The
chancellor spoke to journalists before a meeting with Norwegian
Prime Minister Jens Stoltenberg today north of Berlin.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patrick Donahue in Berlin at 
 pdonahue1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  